<div class="container-fluid">
  <h1 class="mt-4"><a href="/classes">Classes</a></h1>
  <h2>Get requests</h2>
  <p>Example get request that returns all classes in a JSON format:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
     curl 'http://35.234.67.178/classes'
    </code>
  </pre>
  <p>A query can be performed to return a specific class</p>
  <p>Example query:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
     curl 'http://35.234.67.178/classes?class_id=2'
    </code>
  </pre>
  <h2>Post requests</h2>
  <p>Example post request that inserts a new class into the database:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
      curl --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
      --request POST \
      --data '{"class_name":"WDD","class_total_hours":6, "class_difficulty": 10}' \
      http://35.234.67.178/classes
    </code>
  </pre>

</div>
